	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65022895">A source that bears liability for lying. For example, New York Times and Washington Post can be sued for lying in their news reports. Fox News cannot be sued for lying because they stipulate that they are not reporting the truth; they merely opine. <br> <br>This distinction is truly crystal clear. People need to realize this and to start ignoring 100% of "conservative" media, which do nothing but "opine".</div>
	</div>

